-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-1068x678.jpeg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-300x191.jpeg 300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-768x488.jpeg 768w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gwyneth-Paltrow-and-Bill-Clinton-e1711122108525-1536x975.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格温妮丝·帕特洛证实了长期以来的谣言，即美国前总统比尔·克林顿在白宫放映她的电影<em>《艾玛》</em>时睡着了。</p><p>帕特洛在 1996 年由道格拉斯·麦格拉斯执导的简·奥斯汀改编电影中担任主角，并因其表演获得了评论界的好评。</p><p>然而，在最近出现在 YouTube 长剧<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kkx_FiSzbII" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Hot Ones》</em></a>中时，帕特洛明确表示克林顿不是这部电影的粉丝之一。</p><p>由肖恩·埃文斯 (Sean Evans) 主持的<em>《Hot Ones》</em>中，名人们一边回答问题，一边吃着一系列越来越辣的鸡翅。</p><p>当埃文斯问克林顿在白宫放映《<em>艾玛》</em>时睡着的传言是否属实时，帕特洛回答说：“是的——他就在我面前打鼾。”</p><p>她开玩笑地补充道：“我当时想，‘哇，我想这将是一部真正的热门电影。’”但确实如此！所以去你的吧，比尔·克林顿！” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="格温妮丝·帕特洛 (Gwyneth Paltrow) 吃辣鸡翅时充满遗憾热门" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kkx_FiSzbII?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>同样在出现在<em>热门节目</em>中时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-says-you-can-only-make-so-many-good-superhero-movies-3607652">帕特洛建议你“只能制作这么多”优秀的超级英雄电影</a>。</p><p>这位女演员曾在多部<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙</a>电影中与小罗伯特·唐尼饰演的托尼·斯塔克/钢铁侠一起出演“小辣椒”波茨，被问及对导演科德·杰斐逊最近的奥斯卡演讲有何看法。</p><p>杰斐逊凭借电影<em>《美国小说</em>》获得最佳改编剧本奖，并在获奖感言中恳求好莱坞制片人：“与其制作一部价值 2 亿美元的电影，不如尝试制作 20 部价值 1000 万美元的电影。” </p><figure id="attachment_3555464" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3555464" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3555464" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3555464" class="wp-caption-text">格温妮丝·帕特洛。图片来源：红海国际电影节 Daniele Venturelli/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我完全理解他的想法，”帕特洛说。 “您希望获得获得高投资回报率的最佳机会。人们在这些事情上投入了大量资金，他们希望它们能够盈利。”</p><p>她补充道：“但如果我从整个行业的角度来看，超级英雄电影的大力推动……你只能制作出这么多感觉真正原创的好电影，但他们仍然总是试图吸引尽可能多的人，这有时会妨碍质量、特异性或真实观点。”</p><p>格<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-confirms-bill-clinton-fell-alseep-white-house-screening-emma-3608280">温妮丝·帕特洛 (Gwyneth Paltrow) 证实比尔·克林顿 (Bill Clinton) 在白宫放映《艾玛》期间睡着了并“打鼾”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Journey 的《Don’t Stop Believing》被评为有史以来最伟大的歌曲https://www.nme.com/news/music/journeys-dont-stop- believe-has-been-named-the-as-the-biggest-song-of-all-time-3608270?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=旅程-不要停止相信-已被命名为有史以来最大的歌曲Anagricel DuranFri, 22 Mar 2024 15:38:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3608270 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="旅途照片。图片来源：迈克·萨沃亚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们现在正式拥有了音乐史上世界上最伟大的歌曲！祝贺大家，”创始成员兼主音吉他手 Neal Schon 写道</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/journeys-dont-stop-believing-has-been-named-the-as-the-biggest-song-of-all-time-3608270">Journey 的《Don&#39;t Stop Believing》被评为有史以来最伟大的歌曲，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="旅途照片。图片来源：迈克·萨沃亚" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Journey-photo-credit_-Mike-Savoia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/journey">Journey</a>的热门单曲《Don&#39;t Stop Believing》被<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2024/01/31/journeys-dont-stop-believin-is-officially-the-biggest-song-of-all-time/?sh=9ddb90b159a9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《福布斯》</a>评为有史以来最卖座的歌曲，并已达到 18 倍白金销量。</p><p>根据 RIAA（美国唱片工业协会）的数据，《Don&#39;t Stop Believin》现已获得 18 次白金认证，这意味着该曲目在纯销售和其他形式的销售之间已售出超过 1800 万张。仅在美国，消费就像流媒体一样。</p><p>在获得这一荣誉之前，2013 年 5 月，《Don&#39;t Stop Believin》仅达到四白金销量。 Journey 的创始成员兼主音吉他手 Neal Schon 在 X/Twitter 上庆祝了这一成就。 “我们现在正式拥有了音乐史上世界上最伟大的歌曲！恭喜大家<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f446-1f3fb.png" alt="👆🏻" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f64c-1f3fb.png" alt="🙌🏻" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f44c-1f3fb.png" alt="👌🏻" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ，“ 他写了。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Journey - Don&#39;t Stop Believin&#39;（Live 1981：Escape Tour - 2022 高清重制版）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VcjzHMhBtf0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们现在正式拥有了音乐史上世界上最伟大的歌曲！恭喜大家<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/261d-1f3fd.png" alt="☝🏽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/i